SetInCountry: Norway
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: yendi atenea barrera moreno
AuthorCountry: Mexico
Text: It Was fall in Germany and i had save some money.  When suprisedly a friend
  invited me to meet her in Norwey. In that time i barely knew  about Scandinavian
  countries but i took that chance.  I arrived in Trondheim one friday 's evening(
  after that i learned that in Norway weekend almost annyone works). The airport Was
  almost empty, my friend Wasn't There and my mobile Was off. What to do? I search
  for a public phone ( it Wasn't any). Luckly it Was an Office open, and there someone
  borrow me a mobile and i Could contact my friend  and  travel to her aparment on
  my own. If She where not there i did not do anything there because all places are
  closed in weekends.  There for,  that trip i Went to walk around into a  Quiet city
  ...
